post_summaries.description: The image is a top-down shot of a table laden with vegan food at The Farm House, West Malling. Dishes include a vegan lasagna in a cast iron pan, a pizza, a bowl of what appears to be fried potatoes, a salad, and garlic bread. There are also glasses of water and a bottle of white liquid, possibly a drink or sauce. The table is wooden.

The image shows a plate with a homemade vegan Wellington, served with edamame beans, and a sauce. The Wellington is cut in half, revealing a filling that appears to include spinach and other ingredients. The dish is garnished with herbs and spices.
The image shows a vegan lasagna, topped with tomatoes, onions, and what appears to be vegan cheese or a similar substitute.

The image shows a man (vegan_nicholas) drinking from a large mug, presumably coffee or tea, in what appears to be a cafe. There is a plate with a spoon on the table in front of him. The background includes stairs with a "Meet me upstairs" sign, plants, and framed pictures on the wall.
The image is a motivational quote that says "EXECUTION - NOUN - STOP TALKING & PUT IN THE WORK!"

The image shows an overhead shot of two plates of vegan breakfast, each containing vegan sausages, baked beans, mashed avocado, a grilled tomato, and toast. There is also a latte and an iced coffee on the table.
